ontaineruniface_104kai1665702726391.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kai1665702726391.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kai1665702726391.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kai1665702726391\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      open statements\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"kai1665702726391__open_statements_145938\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the number of statements held open by the connector.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kai1665702726391__topic_d47906e1_d47907e1_d47908e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kai1665702726391__d6224e17\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$<var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var>_PARAMS = open statements :</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kai1665702726391__d6224e29\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$<var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var>_PARAMS = os :</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kai1665702726391__topic_d31347e1_d31348e1_d31349e1_d31350e1_d31351e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d262829e80\">\n                        \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kai1665702726391__p_d47918e1_d47919e1_d47920e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>—the number of statements to be held open. If not specified, the default number of statements maintained is 128.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kai1665702726391__topic_d31352e1_d31353e1_d31354e1_d31355e1_d31356e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d262829e92\">\n                        \n Use\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Applies to</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Mnemonic</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Connector Syntax</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">DB2 connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">DB2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$DB2_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBC connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODx</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$ODx_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">MS SQL connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">MSS</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$MSS_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">MySQL connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">MQL</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kai1665702726391__table_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$MQL_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kai1665702726391__topic_d31357e1_d31358e1_d31359e1_d31360e1_d31361e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d262829e233\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kai1665702726391__p_d47927e1_d47928e1_d47929e1\">This option specifies the number of statements that the connector maintains in administration before closing the last recently used one.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7829847\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7829847\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "open statements Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 open statements Specify the number of statements held open by the connector. USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = open statements : Number USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = os : Number Arguments Number —the number of statements to be held open. If not specified, the default number of statements maintained is 128. Use Applies to Mnemonic Connector Syntax DB2 connector DB2 USYS$DB2_PARAMS ODBC connector ODx USYS$ODx_PARAMS MS SQL connector MSS USYS$MSS_PARAMS MySQL connector MQL USYS$MQL_PARAMS Description This option specifies the number of statements that the connector maintains in administration before closing the last recently used one. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}